These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
Food: plum, avocado
Movie-Genre: action, spy
Transport: roller, taxi
1. Movie-Genre:action is on the right of Transport:roller##1
2. Food:avocado is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Food   | avocado    | plum |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | action    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
Pet: chinchilla, goat
Game: whist, billiard
Transport: motorbike, train
1. Transport:train is on the left of Pet:chinchilla##1
2. Game:whist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Pet      | goat  | chinchilla   |
| Game   | billiard | whist  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

